entry.title: Combined summary - Hello
entry.summary: Cezary Dziemian, a member of the Lightning-dev mailing list, reached out to inquire about why he has not received any emails from the list since joining a week ago. Ricardo Filipe responded by stating that there has been no discussion on the list since September 19th and directed Cezary to the archive where he can check for existing discussions. It seems that everything is fine with the mailing list.
